          "",
          "KEY PHRASE:",
          "   compilare un modulo",
          "   = to fill in a form",
          "   (usually by hand, with black pen)"
        ]
      },
      {
        "page": 2,
        "total_pages": 2,
        "content": [
          "NAVIGATING AN UFFICIO PUBBLICO:",
          "",
          "1. Take a number (biglietto)",
          "2. Wait (sometimes hours)",
          "3. Go to the sportello when called",
          "4. Present your documents",
          "5. Get told you need another",
          "   document you didn't bring",
          "6. Come back tomorrow",
          "",
          "USEFUL DOCUMENTS:",
          "   carta d'identità = ID card",
          "   tessera sanitaria = health card",
          "   certificato di residenza",
          "   permesso di soggiorno (foreigners)",
          "",
